INSTALL
=======

* Python 2.7
```
brew install python
```

* Selenium
```
brew install chromedriver
```

HOW TO PREPARE DATASET
======================
NOTE: You can skip this step and proceed directly to RUN section.
Original dataset: https://github.com/w3c/web-platform-tests/tree/master/svg/import

1. Run `prepare-dataset.sh` script to remove revision text from SVGs and convert them into PNGs.
Script `prepare-dataset.sh` calls another script `svg2png.sh` to prepare sample HTML file which will 
load SVG via javascript and renders it in browser and saves it into PNG. 

prepare-dataset.sh
  trim-svg.py
  svg2png.sh

svg2png.sh
  download.py

RUN
===
1. Run `sanity-check.sh` script to verify input data, scripts and everything else.
2. Run script `convert-and-compare A.svg` to conver A.svg into A.png and compare it with a reference PNG file
